{
  "phase": "discovery",
  "instructions": "Look at the plan file (/Users/oliverjaegle/projects/privat/blog/.vibe/development-plan-no-secret-ingredient.md). Define entrance criteria for each phase of the workflow except the initial phase. Those criteria shall be based on the contents of the previous phase. \n      Example: \n      ```\n      ## Design\n\n      ### Phase Entrance Criteria:\n      - [ ] The requirements have been thoroughly defined.\n      - [ ] Alternatives have been evaluated and are documented. \n      - [ ] It's clear what's in scope and out of scope\n      ```\n      \n      IMPORTANT: Once you added reasonable entrance call the whats_next() tool to get guided instructions for the next current phase.\n\nInform the user about the chose workflow: He can visit: https://mrsimpson.github.io/responsible-vibe-mcp/workflows/posts to get detailed information.\n\nNOTE: If the user is communicating in a non-English language, please translate the plan file content to that language while keeping the structure intact, and continue all interactions in the user's language.",
  "plan_file_path": "/Users/oliverjaegle/projects/privat/blog/.vibe/development-plan-no-secret-ingredient.md",
  "conversation_id": "blog-no-secret-ingredient-42geoi",
  "workflow": {
    "name": "posts",
    "description": "A comprehensive workflow for writing posts - from blog posts to short-form content, with research, story development, and multi-platform publishing",
    "initial_state": "discovery",
    "metadata": {
      "complexity": "medium",
      "bestFor": [
        "Blog post writing",
        "Content creation",
        "Article development",
        "Social media content"
      ],
      "useCases": [
        "Writing technical blog posts",
        "Creating marketing content",
        "Developing thought leadership articles"
      ],
      "examples": [
        "Write a tutorial blog post",
        "Create a product announcement",
        "Develop a technical deep-dive article"
      ]
    },
    "states": {
      "discovery": {
        "description": "Research topic, decide format, and analyze competitive landscape",
        "default_instructions": "You are in the discovery phase for post development. This is where you define the foundation of your post.\n\nFocus on understanding the topic and format:\n- Help user decide post format: Ask about goal (quick insight vs deep exploration), topic complexity, available time\n- Research existing content on this topic to identify gaps and opportunities\n- Guide user to articulate personal motivation and unique angle\n- Conduct competitive landscape analysis to avoid duplication\n- Define target audience and platform considerations\n- Gather initial sources and reference materials\n\nWork with the user to establish clear direction before moving to story development.\nUpdate the plan file with discovery progress and key decisions.\n",
        "transitions": [
          {
            "trigger": "discovery_complete",
            "to": "story",
            "additional_instructions": "Discovery complete! ✅ You have clear format decision, unique angle, and research foundation.\n\nUpdate the plan file with story development tasks and mark completed discovery work.\n",
            "transition_reason": "Topic researched and format decided, ready for story structure development"
          },
          {
            "trigger": "abandon_post",
            "to": "discovery",
            "instructions": "Post development abandoned. Clean up any discovery work and prepare for new post topics.\nThe plan file will remain for future reference if needed.\n",
            "additional_instructions": "Post development abandoned. Prepare for new post topics.",
            "transition_reason": "User decided to abandon current post development"
          }
        ]
      },
      "story": {
        "description": "Create narrative structure and story outline",
        "default_instructions": "Working on story development phase. Focus on creating a compelling narrative structure.\n\nKey activities for this phase:\n- Create detailed story outline with clear beginning, middle, end\n- Identify key messages and memorable metaphors/examples\n- Define content scope boundaries to maintain focus and avoid adjacent topics\n- Plan how content will adapt across different platforms\n- Ensure narrative arc matches chosen format (concise for short posts, comprehensive for long-form)\n- Structure content to maintain user's personal voice and conversational style\n\nWork with the user to create a solid story foundation before moving to writing.\nUpdate the plan file with story decisions and structural progress.\n",
        "transitions": [
          {
            "trigger": "story_complete",
            "to": "writing",
            "additional_instructions": "Story complete! ✅ You have a clear narrative structure and content outline.\n\nUpdate the plan file with writing tasks and mark completed story work.\n",
            "transition_reason": "Story structure and outline complete, ready for content creation"
          },
          {
            "trigger": "need_more_discovery",
            "to": "discovery",
            "additional_instructions": "Story development revealed gaps in research or format clarity. Focus on clarifying these foundational aspects.",
            "transition_reason": "Story work revealed need for additional discovery or research"
          },
          {
            "trigger": "abandon_post",
            "to": "discovery",
            "instructions": "Post development abandoned during story phase. Clean up story work and return to discovery.\nThe plan file and any completed work will remain for future reference.\n",
            "additional_instructions": "Post abandoned during story phase. Clean up and prepare for new topics.",
            "transition_reason": "User decided to abandon post during story phase"
          }
        ]
      },
      "writing": {
        "description": "Create the actual post content following story outline",
        "default_instructions": "Working on writing phase. Focus purely on creating engaging content.\n\nKey activities for this phase:\n- Write content following the established story outline\n- Maintain consistent narrative flow and personal voice\n- Create engaging, conversational content in user's style\n- Ensure content length matches chosen format (3-10 lines for short, 2000-5000+ words for long)\n- Stay within defined content scope to avoid adjacent topics\n- Include concrete examples and metaphors as planned\n- Create clear section structure with appropriate headings (for long-form)\n\nFocus on high-quality content creation without visual elements.\nUpdate the plan file with writing progress and content decisions.\n",
        "transitions": [
          {
            "trigger": "writing_complete",
            "to": "illustration",
            "additional_instructions": "Writing complete! ✅ You have solid content that follows your story outline.\n\nUpdate the plan file with illustration tasks and mark completed writing work.\n",
            "transition_reason": "Content creation complete, ready for visual enhancement"
          },
          {
            "trigger": "need_story_revision",
            "to": "story",
            "additional_instructions": "Writing revealed issues with story structure or narrative flow. Focus on refining the story foundation.",
            "transition_reason": "Content creation revealed need for story structure refinement"
          },
          {
            "trigger": "abandon_post",
            "to": "discovery",
            "instructions": "Post development abandoned during writing. Clean up writing work and return to discovery.\nThe plan file and any completed work will remain for future reference.\n",
            "additional_instructions": "Post abandoned during writing phase. Clean up and prepare for new topics.",
            "transition_reason": "User decided to abandon post during writing phase"
          }
        ]
      },
      "illustration": {
        "description": "Create and integrate visual elements",
        "default_instructions": "Working on illustration phase. Focus on visual enhancement of your content.\n\nKey activities for this phase:\n- Identify strategic locations for visual elements\n- Create or source appropriate visuals (screenshots, diagrams, metaphorical images)\n- Ensure visual density matches format (minimal for short posts, comprehensive for long-form)\n- Maintain visual consistency and professional appearance\n- Ensure visuals support and enhance the written content\n- Consider accessibility and platform compatibility\n- Plan visual integration and placement\n\nFocus on creating visuals that enhance rather than distract from the content.\nUpdate the plan file with illustration progress and visual decisions.\n",
        "transitions": [
          {
            "trigger": "illustration_complete",
            "to": "distribution",
            "additional_instructions": "Illustration complete! ✅ You have visually enhanced content ready for publishing.\n\nUpdate the plan file with distribution tasks and mark completed illustration work.\n",
            "transition_reason": "Visual elements complete, ready for SEO optimization and publishing"
          },
          {
            "trigger": "need_more_content",
            "to": "writing",
            "additional_instructions": "Illustration work revealed gaps in written content. Focus on completing the content foundation.",
            "transition_reason": "Visual work revealed need for additional written content"
          },
          {
            "trigger": "abandon_post",
            "to": "discovery",
            "instructions": "Post development abandoned during illustration. Clean up illustration work and return to discovery.\nThe plan file and any completed work will remain for future reference.\n",
            "additional_instructions": "Post abandoned during illustration phase. Clean up and prepare for new topics.",
            "transition_reason": "User decided to abandon post during illustration phase"
          }
        ]
      },
      "distribution": {
        "description": "Optimize for SEO and publish across platforms",
        "default_instructions": "Working on distribution phase. Focus on optimization and multi-platform publishing.\n\nKey activities for this phase:\n- Create compelling, SEO-optimized titles and descriptions\n- Add appropriate tags and metadata for discoverability\n- Adapt content formatting for different platforms (LinkedIn, Medium, HN)\n- Maintain core message while adjusting for platform-specific requirements\n- Conduct final quality review and polish\n- Prepare publishing materials and schedule\n- Execute multi-platform publishing strategy\n\nFocus on maximizing reach while maintaining content quality and consistency.\nUpdate the plan file with distribution progress and publishing decisions.\n",
        "transitions": [
          {
            "trigger": "distribution_complete",
            "to": "discovery",
            "additional_instructions": "Post successfully published. Ready for next post project.",
            "transition_reason": "Post publishing completed successfully, ready for new projects"
          },
          {
            "trigger": "need_final_review",
            "to": "illustration",
            "additional_instructions": "Distribution preparation revealed issues with visuals or content presentation. Focus on final refinements.",
            "transition_reason": "Publishing preparation identified issues requiring visual or content refinement"
          },
          {
            "trigger": "abandon_post",
            "to": "discovery",
            "instructions": "Post development abandoned before distribution. Clean up distribution preparation and return to discovery.\nThe plan file and completed work will remain for future reference.\n",
            "additional_instructions": "Post abandoned before distribution. Clean up and prepare for new topics.",
            "transition_reason": "User decided to abandon post before distribution"
          }
        ]
      }
    }
  },
  "workflowDocumentationUrl": "https://mrsimpson.github.io/responsible-vibe-mcp/workflows/posts"
}
